WEBVTT

00:00:00.211 --> 00:00:01.962
<i>Avonex
Industries announced today</i>

00:00:02.046 --> 00:00:04.924
<i>that AZT has been approved as
the first drug to treat AIDS.</i>

00:00:05.008 --> 00:00:07.977
<i>At the cost of $10,000
per year, per patient,</i>

00:00:08.051 --> 00:00:10.975
<i>AZT is the most expensive
drug ever marketed.</i>

00:00:11.221 --> 00:00:14.522
<i>Avonex stock jumped a whopping
12 percent today on the news.</i>

